The player has the option to select the bet multiplier. Depending on the selected bet, the game behaves differently. The possible values are:
This is the BONUS symbol. It appears on all reels.
SPACE and ENTER buttons on the keyboard can be used to start and stop the spin.
Malfunction voids all pays and plays.

Reels 1 and 6 can have up to 7 symbols. Reels 2, 3, 4 and 5 can have up to 8 symbols. The top row of reels 2 to 5 spins independently from right to left. In total the maximum number of possible ways to win is 200704.

The TUMBLE FEATURE means that after every spin, winning combinations are paid and all winning symbols disappear. The remaining symbols fall to the bottom of the screen and the empty positions are replaced with new symbols coming from above. New symbols are of the same size as the initial spin result, before tumbles.
Special reels are in play during FREE SPINS feature.
Free spins win is awarded to the player after the round completes.
All values are expressed as actual wins in coins.
Tumbling will continue until no more winning combinations appear as a result of a tumble.
When winning on multiple pay ways, all wins are added to the total win.

There are no limits to the number of possible retriggers.
Hit 4 or more BONUS symbols anywhere on the reels to trigger the FREE SPINS ROUND.
The FREE SPINS FEATURE can be instantly triggered from the base game by buying it for 100x current total bet. When the 25x ante bet feature is enabled, the BUY FREE SPINS feature is disabled.

During the free spins round WILD symbols hit with a random multiplier of 2x, 3x or 5x. Every time a WILD is involved in a winning combination it's multiplier is accumulated in a tumble multiplier indicator. All WILD multipliers that hit during a tumble sequence multiply between each other. At the end of the tumble sequence the accumulated multiplier applies to the total win of that tumble sequence.
WILD symbol appears only on reels 2, 3, 4 and 5.
When buying the FREE SPINS feature 4, 5 or 6 BONUS symbols hit randomly awarding 12, 17 or 22 free spins respectively.
Bet multiplier 25x - The chance to win FREE SPINS naturally is doubled, more BONUS symbols are present on the reels but symbol paytable is not affected and they pay as for 20x bet multiplier.
Hit 3 or more BONUS symbols during the feature to win 5 more free spins.

Vetky vhry s nsoben zkladnou stvkou.

Vetky vhry sa pridaj k zostatku hra po tom, o
boli v hre vetky padnutia zo zkladnho toenia.
Celkov vhra pretoen zdarma, v histrii hry, obsahuje celkov vhru cyklu.
Vhra z Pretoenia Zdarma sa pripota k spsobu vyplatenej vhry.
Pre vazn kombinciu plat iba najvyia vhra plat rovnakom spsobe vyplcania.

Vhry, udelen zava doprava za kombincie
susednch symbolov akejkovek vekosti.
Hr m monos vberu nsobitea stvky. V zvislosti od zvolenej stvky sa hra sprva inak. Mon hodnoty s:
Toto je symbol BONUS. Objavuje sa na vetkch valcoch.
Tlaidl SPACE a ENTER na klvesnici mu by pouit na spustenie a zastavenie pretoenia.
Porucha zru vetky platby a hry.
Valce 1 a 6 mu ma a 7 symbolov. Valce 2, 3, 4 a 5 mu ma a 8 symbolov. Vrchn rad valcov 2 a 5 sa to nezvisle sprava doava. Celkov maximlny poet monch spsobov vhry je 200704.

FUNKCIA PADNUTIE znamen, e pri kadom toen s vyplcan vhern kombincie a vetky vhern symboly zmizn. Zostvajce symboly spadn na spodok obrazovky a przdne miesta sa nahradia novmi symbolmi prichdzajcimi zhora. Nov symboly maj rovnak vekos ako vsledok poiatonho toenia pred padnutiami.
Poas funkcie TOEN ZDARMA s v hre pecilne valce.
Po dokonen kola je hrovi udelen vhra pretoen zdarma.
Vetky hodnoty s vyjadren ako skuton vhry v minciach.
Padnutie bude pokraova, a km sa neprestan zobrazova alie kombincie, ako vsledok padnutia.
Pri vazstve pri viacerch spsoboch vyplcania sa vetky vhry pripotaj k celkovej vhre.
Maximlna vhern iastka je obmedzen na {0}x stvky. Ak celkov vhra KOLA TOEN ZDARMA Dosiahne {1}x, kolo sa okamite ukon, vhra je udelen a vetky toenia zdarma sa stratia.
Pre poet monch optovnch spaov neexistuj iadne obmedzenia.
6x symbol BONUS vyplca celkom 100x celkovej stvky
5x symbol BONUS vyplca celkom 20x celkovej stvky
Zasiahnite 4 alebo viac symbolov BONUS kdekovek na obrazovke, aby ste spustili KOLO TOEN ZADARMO.
FUNKCIU TOEN ZADARMO je mon spusti okamite v zkladnej hre zakpenm za 100x aktulnej celkovej stvky. Ke je povolen funkcia 25x ante stvka, je funkcia NKUP TOEN ZADARMO deaktivovan.
RTP hry pri pouit "KPI TOENIA ZDARMA" je {0}%
RTP hry pri pouit "ANTE STVKY" je {0}%

Poas kola toen zadarmo bud zasiahnut symboly WILD s nhodnm nsobiteom 2x, 3x alebo 5x. Zakadm, ke je symbol WILD zasiahnut na obrazovke, jeho nsobite je akumulovan v indiktore padania nsobiteov. Vetky nsobitele WILD, ktor s zasiahnut poas sekvencie padania, sa medzi sebou vynsobia. Na konci sekvencie padnut sa akumulovan nsobite pouije na celkov vhru danej sekvencie padnut.
4x symbol BONUS vyplca celkom 5x celkovej stvky
Symbol WILD sa objavuje na valcoch 2, 3, 4 a 5.
Pri zakpen funkcie TOEN ZADARMO bud nhodne zasiahnut 4, 5 alebo 6 symbolov BONUS udeujce 12, 17 alebo 22 toen zadarmo.
Nsobite stvky 25x - anca vyhra TOENIA ZADARMO sa prirodzene zdvojnsob, na valcoch je prtomnch viacero symbolov BONUS, ale tabuka vhier so symbolmi nie je ovplyvnen a plat ako pri 20x nsobitea stvok.
Poas funkcie zasiahnite 3 alebo viac symbolov BONUS, aby ste vyhrali 5 alch toen zadarmo.
VETKY SYMBOLY WILD VYNSOBIA CELKOV VHRU PADANV TOENIACH ZADARMO
K vhre vplaty sa pridaj toenia zadarmo a bonusov vhry.
Maximlna vhern suma je obmedzen na {0}x stvky okrem Jackpotu. Ak celkov vhra kola TOEN ZDARMA dosiahne {1}x stvky, kolo sa okamite skon, udel sa vhra a vetky zostvajce toenia zdarma prepadn.
